Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Place&Name==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.98,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由行星同盟首都 海尼森波裏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.59,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住宅街 楓樹嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:09.21,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國防委員 優布·特留尼西特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:44.49,ezc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍官候補生 達斯提·亞典波羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.98,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heinessenpolis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.59,eze,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maple Hill
